4" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3487404" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/cyberpunk-2077-free-update-making-massive-changes-to-the-game-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3487404" class="wp-caption-text"> 《赛博朋克 2077》图片来源：CD Projekt Red</figcaption></figure><p>该团队能够分享的是，2.0 更新中改进了执法系统并改进了敌人的人工智能。马林诺夫斯基继续说道，汽车追逐会导致“路障、激烈的枪战，当然还有 MaxTac”。</p><p> “警察会根据你的体温水平做出相应反应，设置额外的陷阱，试图将你撞离道路，一旦他们确信你已经完全进入网络精神病状态，最终就会召唤大枪，”他解释道，并补充说，更多信息更新2.0即将到来。</p><p> <em>《赛博朋克 2077：幻影自由》</em>将于 9 月 26 日登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> ，届时 2.0 更新也将免费推出。</p><p>一个月前，开发商决定<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-cd-projekt-red-drops-around-100-staff-3473656">未来的项目不再需要大约百分之九的员工</a>。 “我们已经知道明年我们不会为他们提供其他机会，”首席执行官 Adam Kiciński 说道。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-update-2-0-will-make-massive-changes-to-the-game-for-free-3487